lyrics:
[verse]
He wakes up alone in a cold empty bed
Memories of her laughter fill his confused head
The silence shouts louder, can't escape the dread
His heart torn apart, as another tear is shed

[chorus]
Oh, he's lost, lost without her by his side
Drowning in the shadows with nowhere to hide
In this dark abyss, he's screaming out her name
But she's gone, gone forever, it's driving him insane
